deInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\"><div class=\"ss\"></div>\n<div class=\"ss1\"></div>\n<img src=\"../../images/weixintupian_20210224160842.jpg\">\n  \n  <div class=\"current wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n<div class=\"clearfix container\">\n    <div class=\"pull-left banner-tt\">\n\n\n\n航空宇航工程系</div>\n    <div class=\"pull-left nav-b\">                <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk.htm\">师资情况</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\">师资信息</a>\n                &gt;\n                <a href=\"../../szqk/szxx/hkyhgcx.htm\">航空宇航工程系</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"clearfix container\"><ul class=\"pull-right banner-ul clearfix\">\n    \n    <li><a href=\"../../szqk/ys.htm\" title=\"院士\">院士</a></li>\n\n    \n    <li class=\"active\"><a href=\"../../szqk/szxx.htm\" title=\"师资信息\">师资信息</a></li>\n\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n  </div>\n\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n<div>\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format2.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n\n<div style=\"background: #fff;\">\n\n       <div class=\"teach-top wow fadeInUp animated\" style=\"visibility: visible; animation-name: fadeInUp;\">\n            <div class=\"teach-top-img\"><img src=\"/__local/D/F3/E8/A6ABC7B00113E61D1CDF5D6F004_88E3A06A_1141E.jpg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-name\"><a>程彬</a></div>\n            <div class=\"teacher-p\">\n                <div class=\"row\">\n                    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\n                                    <p>职称：助理教授</p>\n                                  \n                                    <p>E-mail address：bincheng@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div> \n        <div id=\"vsb_content_2\"><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">个人简介</div><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">程彬，男，1995年生于河南镇平，航空宇航科学与技术博士，清华大学航天航空学院助理教授、博导。主要从事地外天体探测、空间资源开发等方向，在Nature Astronomy等国际顶级期刊发表多篇论文，研究工作被Nature、Science作为研究亮点报告，受到央视新闻、科技日报、BBC、CNN等专访，参与我国天问二号小行星探测任务与动能撞击偏转小行星在轨验证任务。入选北京市青年人才托举工程、博士后创新人才支持计划，获得北京市自然科学二等奖、北京市优秀博士论文奖等奖励；所指导研究生获清华大学特等奖学金、国家自然科学基金青年学生基础研究项目(博士研究生)、国家奖学金等奖励。</p>\n<p>课题组长期招收博士和硕士研究生、联合培养研究生和博士后研究人员，欢迎热爱科学、愿意投身科研的有志青年联系。</p>\n<p>通讯地址：清华大学蒙民伟科技大楼N923室，100084</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">邮箱: bincheng@tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n</div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">教育背景</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">2012.8-2016.7 清华大学 工程力学与航天航空工程学士</p>\n<p>2016.8-2021.6 清华大学 航空宇航科学与技术博士</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2019.9-2020.9 美国亚利桑那大学 联培博士</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">工作履历</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">2021.7-2024.7 清华大学 博士后</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2024.8-至今 清华大学 助理教授</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究领域</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">地外天体探测、空间资源开发</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">研究概况</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">1. 地外天体动力学演化：以动力学的角度，解释深空探测任务中发现的各种奇特现象，从而回答行星系统起源这一科学谜题，指导探测器设计与探测方案制定。代表性工作：揭示了陀螺型小行星的快速自旋成形机制，发现了地球准卫星可能来自月球GB撞击坑，参与我国天问二号与小行星撞击防御任务。</p>\n<p>2. 地外机器人设计与控制：克服乃至利用地外极端特殊环境，设计新构态的锚定、攀爬、移动机器人，开发智能自主控制算法。代表性工作：提出了利用弱引力环境的弹跳移动巡视方案，提出了适应松散碎石堆结构的根鞘式植物仿生锚定装置。</p>\n<p>3. 地外资源采运力学：针对水冰提取、金属冶炼等典型场景，揭示自然/人工复合力场下混合成分资源采运力学特性及其运动规律。代表性工作：提出了月球极区水冰微波采冰方案并进行了实验/数值模拟验证。</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">正在组织2029年Apophis小行星快速飞掠与采样任务，千年一遇的航天机遇，欢迎加入！</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">奖励与荣誉</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">北京市自然科学二等奖(3/3)</p>\n<p>北京市青年人才托举工程</p>\n<p>博士后创新人才支持计划</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">北京市优秀博士论文奖</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">学术成果</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">近年来代表性论文：</p>\n<p>1. Jiao, Yifei; <b>Cheng, Bin*</b>; Huang, Yukun; Asphaug, Erik; Gladman, Brett; Malhotra, Renu; Michel, Patrick; Yu, Yang; Baoyin, Hexi*; Asteroid Kamo‘oalewa’s journey from the lunar Giordano Bruno crater to Earth 1:1 resonance, Nature Astronomy, 2024, 8(7): 819-826</p>\n<p>2. <b>Cheng, Bin</b>; Yu, Yang*; Asphaug, Erik; Michel, Patrick; Richardson, Derek C.; Hirabayashi, Masatoshi; Yoshikawa, Makoto; Baoyin, Hexi*; Reconstructing the formation history of top-shaped asteroids from the surface boulder distribution, Nature Astronomy, 2021, 5(2): 134-138</p>\n<p>3. <b>Cheng, Bin*</b>; Baoyin, Hexi ; Structural stability of China’s asteroid mission target 2016 HO3 and its possible structure, Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society, 2024, 534(2): 1376-1393</p>\n<p>4. Wang, Qiujun; <b>Cheng, Bin*</b>; Baoyin, Hexi; Piao, Ying ; LBM-DEM modeling of particle-fluid interactions on active small solar bodies, Astronomy Astrophysics, 2024, 691: A265</p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">5. Jiao, Yifei; <b>Cheng, Bin</b>*; Baoyin, Hexi*; Optimal Kinetic-Impact Geometry for Asteroid Deflection Exploiting Delta-V Hodograph, Journal of Guidance, Control, and Dynamics, 2023, 46(2): 382-389</p></div><div class=\"xq-title wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">人才培养</div><div class=\"jl-txt wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\"><p class=\"vsbcontent_start\">所指导研究生获清华大学特等奖学金、国家自然科学基金青年学生基础研究项目(博士研究生)、国家奖学金等奖励。</p></div></div>\n\n     </div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"footer wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <div class=\"friends-box wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"friends-left\">友情链接</div>\n    <a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/\" title=\"\" onclick=\"_addDynClicks(&quot;wburl&quot;, 1696534067, 71220)\">清华大学</a>\n\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"clearfix wow fadeInUp\" style=\"visibility: hidden; animation-name: none;\">\n        <div class=\"pull-left footer-logo\">                            <img src=\"../../images/logo.png\">\n</div>\n        <div class=\"pull-right footer-txt\"><!-- 版权内容请在本组件\"内容配置-版权\"处填写 -->\n<p>版权所有 © 清华大学京ICP备15006448号 京公网安备 110402430053 号&nbsp;</p><p>推荐ie8以上谷歌等浏览器浏览网页</p><p>联系方式：电话：010-62782434&nbsp; &nbsp;传真：010-62792407</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n<script src=\"../../js/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/bootstrap.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/slick.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/wow.min.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../js/common.js\"></script>\n<script>\nif (!(/msie [6|7|8|9]/i.test(navigator.userAgent))){\n  new WOW().init();\n};\n            \n       function stopPropagation(e) {\n            var ev = e || window.event;\n            if (ev.stopPropagation) {\n                ev.stopPropagation();\n            }\n         